narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: You learn a lot about Japanese Politics, a little less about the Japanese Economy. Interesting course, not too heavy of a workload for a seminar.
This is an excellent class with a really good professor. Definitely take it if you are interested in politics, economics, or simply understanding the current events of your time!
If you're interested in Japanese Politics take this class. Professor Saito is very knowledgeable about the inner workings of the Japanese Political system and is very accessible to students.
